{"tid":2420961,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能有三種食材夾埋會好難食，但係其中任意兩個會夾","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T23:54:06.000Z","uid":25073,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5bed3d6a58219cdb7e2e0674f8c4dbfd25d3c7","tid":2420961,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.atlasobscura.com/articles/the-incompatible-food-triad-is-the-most-delicious-philosophical-problem-of-our-time\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlasobscura.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-incompatible-food-triad-is-the-most-delicious-philosophical-problem-of-our-time&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=1e7b9c19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.atlasobscura.com/articles/the-incompatible-food-triad-is-the-most-delicious-philosophical-problem-of-our-time</a><br />\n簡單嚟講<br />\n舉三種食材，例如薄荷、羊架、同朱古力<br />\n三樣夾埋我覺得會好難食<br />\n但係薄荷朱古力我諗大家都食過<br />\n西餐用薄荷幫羊架辟羶<br />\n<a href=\"https://trufflerose.pixnet.net/blog/post/27393492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrufflerose.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F27393492&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=ce25eab2\" target=\"_blank\">https://trufflerose.pixnet.net/blog/post/27393492</a><br />\n的確有食譜會用朱古力配羊架<br />\n但係都有食譜係教你將三樣嘢加埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知道全能嘅連登仔有冇可能諗到有三種食材符合到我topic嘅要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea73f9089dad5d5a799a21e41845975269733beb","tid":2420961,"uid":60527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"3色豆"},{"pid":"74f536e852d0d9bd7cb51854d37a5d7b4da32a8b","tid":2420961,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea73f9089dad5d5a799a21e41845975269733beb","tid":2420961,"uid":60527,"like":6,"dislike